item.title: CVE-2021-20350|2024-08-03T17:37:23.926Z -- ibm -- rational%20quality%20manager
item.description: IBM Engineering products are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 194707.
